{"tid":410054,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"車保羅腳踏實地做雜工　隨地遺煙頭賺埋唔夠罰","createTime":"2017-09-22T14:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T16:15:06.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"128d3ed771a2a32a7f0720f6c4444dafc083c5ba","tid":410054,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T14:43:05.000Z","msg":"發佈日期：2017年9月22日<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IvDCHAvGC-Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIvDCHAvGC-Q&d=xPvb5zCE1hvAv7d1YEpdmP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=46eb270f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IvDCHAvGC-Q</a><br />\n車保羅事關近年常被傳死訊，但現在仍然在生，可能因為少了在幕前出現，大家才會以為他不在人世，其實他只是轉行而已!<br />\n<br />\n打不死的車保羅，03年被無綫解僱、之後外孫女車禍慘死、還試過因失業而要攞綜援。生活潦倒到連媽媽過身都要問朋友借錢辦喪禮。最差的生活他前半生經歷過，今時今日他更享受腳踏實地的生活。雖然他仍然熱愛演戲，但都只是間中客串下，無再視演戲為終身職業。<br />\n<br />\n現在他在博愛醫院董事局做雜工，生活還算過得去。這天他身穿一身公司制服就知他正在上班了。他6呎4吋高的身型在人群中還蠻顯眼的，身旁的路人都有看他幾眼，不知有沒有人認到他呢?<br />\n<br />\n送完貨走到路邊等公司車，正所謂&ldquo;吊頸都要抖下氣&rdquo;，他當然都要吸口香煙放鬆下。咦?雖然你現在有份穩定工作，但是你也不想被人罰一千五吧!下次不要亂扔煙頭了!"},{"pid":"4c86dd7898b0caeadc685eccf4a5d3fde3ac16f6","tid":410054,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T14:57:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1e3443b984e3798e3089471e67ba89cf651ee2","tid":410054,"uid":50663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T15:01:59.000Z","msg":"成日係元朗見到佢"},{"pid":"b2b99418b562c0139588295d4b3614c1a2cb7e6b","tid":410054,"uid":35313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T15:18:46.000Z","msg":"早排先做viuTV套詭探"},{"pid":"4fe3d34d41b951675c5d929f8bcda06ec10794cc","tid":410054,"uid":8795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T15:22:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日係元朗見到佢</blockquote><br />\n日日都坐係呂廷門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9af681d5be413220ce1cbe4b55394c086d5a2e2","tid":410054,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T15:34:20.000Z","msg":"記得有個post話鼻高就一定靚仔<br />\n<br />\n跟住有人貼左佢張相出黎"},{"pid":"3ac82661b41a33c47d307dbb1361124a02faaf4e","tid":410054,"uid":88120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T15:35:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c20e26477aa9fb5e4ec3c07f89048e642ac39938","tid":410054,"uid":50663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T15:37:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成日係元朗見到佢</blockquote><br />\n日日都坐係呂廷門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 由朝坐到晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c7fa3593f4c0544100a0216f481c27648746e36","tid":410054,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T15:39:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成日係元朗見到佢</blockquote><br />\n日日都坐係呂廷門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成日見佢坐三上後面條巷仔"},{"pid":"f648046cb7459f48ee4d216df911da235258681c","tid":410054,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:17:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b356782f5ad56aa122ee3e2432a09082143ce2","tid":410054,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:08:40.000Z","msg":"打不死"},{"pid":"d42cc83ee428aaf3e8e21bb855733717069c9d8b","tid":410054,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:12:40.000Z","msg":"03年被無綫解僱、之後外孫女車禍慘死、還試過因失業而要攞綜援。生活潦倒到連媽媽過身都要問朋友借錢辦喪禮。<br />\n<br />\n本來見到覺得陰公<br />\n<br />\n之後見到掉煙頭就覺得<br />\n原來抵既"},{"pid":"8b4a39e68d6126e257a19279cfea2eca32fe2a64","tid":410054,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:13:41.000Z","msg":"馬死落地行 真男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad41405ac41fcda6feeb4348cdc